Name: ENTRY
checklistText:
<size=24>ENTRY</size>

NOTE: TR will vary depending on your entry angle.

<size=22>AT TR +14:30</size>
CONTROL S/C ATTITUDES TO:
	0 DEG YAW
	170 DEG ROLL
	HORIZON AT TOP OF WINDOW

<size=22>AT TR + 19:00 (400K FEET)</size>
AFTER ROLL NEEDLE DEFLECTION:
	CONTROL S/C ATT TO BACKUP BANK ANGLE & DAMP PITCH AND YAW RATES
	ATTITUDE CONTROL - RATE CMD (RE-ENT)
